Dried spaghetti being measured with a "spaghetti measure". 1 portion of dried pasta equals 120 grams (4.1 oz), twice the amount of 1 serving on the package (12 mm circle or 60 g.). The measure can portion out 1, 2, 3, or 4 servings based on the diameter of the circle. This spaghetti is an enriched macaroni product made with 100% semolina.
